# Ajaia Docs — Cursor rules summary

Collaborative document editor (Next.js 15 + TipTap + Prisma/SQLite). Full rules in `.cursor/rules/`; reference docs in `.cursor/docs/`.

## Stack

Next.js 15 · React 19 · TypeScript 5 · Prisma 6 · SQLite · TipTap 2 · jose JWT · Zod · Vitest · Tailwind 4

## Hard rules

- API routes: `getSession()` → Zod validate → `lib/` + prisma → JSON response
- Document access via `getDocumentAccess()` / `isDocumentOwner()` only
- No `prisma` in client components
- TipTap via `DocumentEditorLoader` with `ssr: false`
- Imports use `@/` alias
- No `any`; no secrets in repo

## Tests

```bash
npm test
```

